README
# LockBit Indicators of Compromise (IOCs)

This directory contains a structured collection of Indicators of Compromise (IOCs) identified during the threat intelligence analysis of LockBit ransomware.

IOC Categories

Network Indicators
- Known malicious domains
- Cloud storage and exfiltration services
- Remote access software frequently abused by affiliates

Host Indicators
- Credential dumping tools
- Discovery and enumeration utilities
- Living-off-the-land binaries (LOLBins)

Defense Evasion
- Antivirus and EDR disabling utilities
- Event log clearing
- Software packing and obfuscation

Behavioral Indicators
- Volume shadow copy deletion
- Mass file encryption
- Large outbound data transfers
- RDP and SMB lateral movement
- Ransom note creation

